{"tid":1598553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大專代表團要你幫手呀喂！","createTime":"2019-09-27T13:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T11:31:53.000Z","uid":36467,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f7516d0b821f2291ae4e63a35d3ea6eee9eee7d8","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:56:22.000Z","msg":"有班學生幾個月唔讀書，日日出訪見政要，成功加辣民主法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但sir this way唔係冇代價，機票住宿全部都係錢，好多都係自己俾住先咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n接下落黎依班做實事嘅人重有好多地方要去，好多人要見。冇香港人support佢地做唔到幾耐架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家得九萬重差好多<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://t.me/hkiad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkiad&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=63c8800b\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkiad</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃｜HKIAD Crowdfunding Plan】<br />\n(Please scroll down for English version)<br />\n<br />\n我哋係香港大專學界國際事務代表團（HKIAD），成立於今年7月。代表團由十二間大專院校學生會代表組成。<br />\n<br />\n我哋曾經喺八月舉辦過「英美港盟主權在民集會」，亦有派出代表去到世界各地進行民間外交及遊說工作。<br />\n<br />\n我哋而家發起眾籌計畫，目標籌款300萬港元，以支援舉行活動、民間外交之費用。<br />\n<br />\n請大家多多支持！<br />\n<br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=695b3663\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\nWe are Hong Kong Higher Institutions International Affairs Delegation (HKIAD). The delegation was founded in this July and formed by 12 Students&rsquo; Unions of Higher Institution of Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nA rally has been held by us in this August, namely &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong, Power to the People Rally&rdquo;. Also, we have sent several delegations to different parts of world to do civic diplomatic work and lobbying.<br />\n<br />\nWe are now initiating a Crowdfunding plan, aiming at raising 3,000,000 HKD in order to support our work in organizing events and civic diplomacy.<br />\n<br />\nPlease do not hesitate to show your support!<br />\n<br />\nDonation Link：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=695b3663\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a>"},{"pid":"d816e344512d9faa4c98c08d449571e8d8c9ad5d","tid":1598553,"uid":130214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:57:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2bf7b9cac5953d26ceacf9deba2e10f8410442","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:57:05.000Z","msg":"對唔住我柒咗，重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見佢地連登冇pub想幫吓手"},{"pid":"65b12811c5a491352c7a1f0009be630b8ef35fb1","tid":1598553,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:57:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a77d8fe75a60b90320d30e2053557fd52ede32c","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"9d1865e090620a0004d38983a91ee7032fd0bebc","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"sir this way!"},{"pid":"9ab1185a17cccdbc276f07e7e514d69e570676cd","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4121f3090ad83327d1ab11981febf7ca34400f","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbb4128ac9de511a69840cd0f56ccf1fecd7968","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"80b79bf04f64f9d4145438a914b658aa1f6424ac","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:02:15.000Z","msg":"5連了，推唔到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd82df1d3d4ee5863a0f92365bd0f8d8d5b77cde","tid":1598553,"uid":244901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43f952d15624953621ca6042b33ce8e1a4b83574","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:04:19.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"73679e79be213369143848ed32d6f74a2adc3a40","tid":1598553,"uid":99172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:05:07.000Z","msg":"有冇得詳細講下個300萬會用黎做咩<br />\n眾籌要寫得詳細啲<br />\n唔想又搞到612咁比人屌黎屌去"},{"pid":"457c4dc18ac4225a2d08dc89e991c674b930d911","tid":1598553,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"913bdc03f105e8dd2d53945c6f31ff6e9930f48f","tid":1598553,"uid":247708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:06:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"edebbf6cfd00c9fdeb372d6a4cdefb510338d57c","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"73679e79be213369143848ed32d6f74a2adc3a40","tid":1598553,"uid":99172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:05:07.000Z","msg":"有冇得詳細講下個300萬會用黎做咩<br />\n眾籌要寫得詳細啲<br />\n唔想又搞到612咁比人屌黎屌去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"佢地民間外交做咗好多嘢。<br />\n飛去見人係一part,呢到要好多錢。<br />\n另外又要team人做report俾政要睇。<br />\n重有之前搞集會都係錢。<br />\n<br />\n我諗因為時局變得太快佢地都未知黎緊可以飛去邊，同邊個國家想見佢地，未寫到好詳細。但佢地發言人話一定會公開財務細節。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKHIIAD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKHIIAD%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=e91ee080\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKHIIAD/</a><br />\n<br />\n或者你可以去佢地fb page問吓"},{"pid":"8929f16d69aa2108cf5ae7653076cbf594f1663a","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:16:23.000Z","msg":"唔做標題黨就推唔起&hellip;點搞"},{"pid":"0aff9300566603198cd2cdbd49fe1da5e526d68e","tid":1598553,"uid":25425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"幫推新post"},{"pid":"fae9f34f340494b82f73106c2bb353be819d0d66","tid":1598553,"uid":25425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1170114ecdc40027eae7191ba493d15cfc939a12","tid":1598553,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae899caf02b512b23b42a71e1038274327fa2818","tid":1598553,"uid":144542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a94256ca8aea48ca92ed129ca7df9af4deeed3b","tid":1598553,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:40:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90908d6810da0de1ded3e663da223d80af565202","tid":1598553,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:40:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a93b890f45d19f228d5a2151982424be8ce83375","tid":1598553,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:40:51.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"cce0e7025e7532277ec2811ed3f036c63b10f25e","tid":1598553,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:40:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}